item.title: CVE-2024-1274|2024-04-02T05:15:41.805Z -- Unknown -- My Calendar
item.description: The My Calendar WordPress plugin before 3.4.24 does not sanitise and escape some parameters, which could allow users with a role as low as Subscriber to perform Cross-Site Scripting attacks (depending on the permissions set by the admin)
